title: Charles McPherson Interview | Part 1 |"San Diego Profiles"
description: Part 1 of an interview with alto saxophonist Charles McPherson. The interview was hosted by Brian McMahon at San Diego City College as part of the "San Diego Profiles" series. The interview date was January 30, 2003.
